## Dependencies on Qt5 and cereal
apt install qtbase5-dev qt5-qmake
apt install libcereal-dev

## Build instructions
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make dijkstras_train

## Rules & Controls
Left-click to place board pieces.
Right-click to remove board pieces.
Terminators and junctions can be placed on any unoccupied square.
Tracks can only be placed alongside a junction, terminator, or another track.
Trains can be placed on tracks.
Clicking on a train flips its direction.

Try loading some of the examples provided to get started, or create your own!
